    "content": "\u201cBecause Of You\u201d by Kelly Clarkson\r\n\r\nEverything in this song is quarter notes, and you let each note ring.  You\u2019ll have to\r\nlisten to the song to know when to play each part, and there are certain parts that\r\nrequire you to hold only for a certain period of time, which is hard to translate into\r\ntabs, so yeah, just listen to the song a few times to get the timing down.\r\n\r\n[tab]Intro:\r\nG|-----------------|\r\nD|-----------------|\r\nA|-----------------| don\u2019t play\r\nE|-----------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]Verse 1:\r\nG|----------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nD|----------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nA|---------3---3-----------6---6-----------3---3-----------6---6--|\r\nE|-4---4-----------1---1-----------4---4-----------1---1----------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]G|-------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nD|-------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nA|---------3---3-----------6---6-----------3---3-----------6---6/12--|\r\nE|-4---4-----------1---1-----------4---4-----------1---1-------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]Chorus:\r\nG|----------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nD|----------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nA|---------4---4---6---6---6---6-----------4---4---6---6---6---6--|\r\nE|-1---1---------------------------1---1--------------------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]G|----------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nD|----------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nA|---------4---4---6---6---6---6-----------4---4---6---6---6---6--|\r\nE|-1---1---------------------------1---1--------------------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]G|--------------------------------------------------------|\r\nD|--------------------------------------------------------|\r\nA|-4---4---3---3---6---6---6---6---4---4---4---4---6---6--|\r\nE|--------------------------------------------------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]Verse 2:\r\nG|----------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nD|----------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nA|---------3---3-----------6---6-----------3---3-----------6---6--|\r\nE|-4---4-----------1---1-----------4---4-----------1---1----------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]G|-------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nD|-------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nA|---------3---3-----------6---6-----------3---3-----------6---6/12--|\r\nE|-4---4-----------1---1-----------4---4-----------1---1-------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]Chorus:\r\nG|----------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nD|----------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nA|---------4---4---6---6---6---6-----------4---4---6---6---6---6--|\r\nE|-1---1---------------------------1---1--------------------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n[tab]G|----------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nD|----------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nA|---------4---4---6---6---6---6-----------4---4---6---6---6---6--|\r\nE|-1---1---------------------------1---1--------------------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]G|----------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nD|----------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nA|-4---4---3---3---6---6---6---6---4---4---4---4---6---6---6---6--|\r\nE|----------------------------------------------------------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]Interlude:\r\nG|----------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nD|----------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nA|-3---3-----------6---6---6---6---3---3-----------6---6---6---6--|\r\nE|---------1---1---------------------------1---1------------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]G|-------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nD|------------